title: Caring, Professional Management Team, Easy Access To IH-45
posting_body: ['WELCOME TO CRICKET HOLLOW', 'A charming community consisting of spacious 2 bedroom – 2 bath and 3 bedroom – 2 bath apartment homes.', 'Convenient to Lake Conroe, Cricket Hollow is located on FM 1097, ½ of a mile west of the Interstate 45 N.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 20', 'OR Text', '20', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1068 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Enhanced 9 Foot High Ceilings', '- Choice Of Distinctive 2 And 3 Bedroom Residences', '- Dishwasher And Stainless Double Sink With Disposal', '- Electric Range With Oven And Built-In Microwave', '- Mini-Blind Window Coverings', '- Entertainment Serving Bar', '- Private Patio Or Balcony', '- Frost-Free Refrigerator With Ice Maker', '- Roomy Open Kitchen Area', '- Spacious Cabinetry', 'And Large Pantry', '- Ceiling Fans With Light Fixture', 'In Living And Bedrooms', '- Full Size Washer-Dryer Connections In Every Unit', '- Extra Outside Storage', '- Wide Spacious Countertops', 'Community Amenities', '- Easy Access To IH-45', '- Internet Access Computers & Print Station', '- Organized Services & Resident Activities', '- Inviting Sparkling Pool', '- Business Center', '- Complimentary Office Services', '- Reserved Covered Parking Available', '- Large Community Center', '- Caring, Professional Management Team', '- Equipped Playground', '- Excellent Willis Island Schools', '- Minutes from Lake Conroe & other nearby Recreation', '- Laundry Facility', '- On-Site Maintenance', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-4:00PM', 'Cricket Hollow Apartments', '9700 FM 1097, Willis, TX, 77318', 'JeW7fZ5XtKP']
